\textbf{simple summary about latex}\\
L is a document preparation system for typsetting program .it is used to create different types of document sructures.A L file (.tex)is created using any text editor (vim,emacs,gedit,etc.).There are also many L IDEs like kile,TexStudio,ect..
\end{abstract}
